headline: Block Adds Amazon, QuickBooks, Uber Eats As Partner Ecosystem Nears 1,000
summary: Block (NYSE: XYZ) ticked up in Friday premarket on its expanded seller partner ecosystem ahead of Feb. 26 earnings, though the stock's momentum remains weak versus the tech sector.
